I"y<p>The <code>pocketcasts</code> sensor platform lets you monitor how many unplayed episodes you have of your favorite podcasts at <a href="https://play.pocketcasts.com/">Pocket Casts</a>.</p>
<h2>Configuration</h2>
<div class='note warning'>
<p>This integration requires a <a href="https://www.pocketcasts.com/plus/">Pocket Casts + Plus</a> subscription to work!</p>
</div>
<p>To enable this sensor, add the following lines to your <code>configuration.yaml</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
sensor:
  - platform: pocketcasts
    username: YOUR_USERNAME
    password: YOUR_PASSWORD
</code></pre>
<div class="config-vars">
  <h3><a class="title-link" name="configuration-variables" href="#configuration-variables"></a> Configuration Variables</h3>
  <dl class=''><dt><a class='title-link' name='username' href='#username'></a> username</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>The username to access the PocketCasts service.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='password' href='#password'></a> password</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>The password for the given username.</p>
</span></p></dd></dl>
</div>
